CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 23, 1958, pg. B2, reads: "'Deejay Mr. B' - Pittsburgh-born crooner Billy Eckstine took time out from his chores at the Holiday House to visit and don the attire of disc jockey for the Jay Michael Show on Radio Station WCAE. 'Mr. B' is drawing crowds in his first homecoming engagement in nine years. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Billy Eckstine wearing earphones and holding his album talking into WCAE radio station microphone with banner in background inscribed "WCAE 1250 on Your Dial"
